    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-09-21T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-09-21T18:00:00-05:00" n="897"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d897">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">501.BB Korea/9–2148: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Embassy in France</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-09-21T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 21, 1948—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Gadel1">Gadel</gloss> 34. For Jessup. Paul-Boncour states
                    consensus members <gloss target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss>, now drafting report
                    Lake Success, is that they shd proceed Paris <hi rend="italic">en bloc</hi> to
                    report <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> and be available consultation. Points
                    out additional advantage <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> might refer to them
                    such Korean reps as not accredited by Govt <gloss target="#t_Rep1">Rep</gloss>
                    Korea. He indicates Secretariat (meaning Sobolev) wishes extinguish <gloss
                        target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss> and will try refuse authorization travel
                    Paris. He proposes introduce into <gloss target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss>
                    draft resolution calling for latter’s presence Paris, land appears confident its
                    passage unanimous vote members present. Foregoing without prejudice continuance
                        <gloss target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss> seat and rump representation
                    Seoul.</p>
                <p>In event you approached by <gloss target="#t_SYG1">SyG</gloss> or his rep for US
                    views presence <gloss target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss> Paris, you shd reply
                    that as <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> Res directed <gloss
                        target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss> report <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>,
                    and as <gloss target="#t_UNTCOK1">UNTCOK</gloss> master own procedure, we would
                    think it appropriate its decision this sense be implemented, aside from valuable
                    services this experienced body may be able offer <gloss target="#t_GA1"
                        >GA</gloss> if present as group.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
